The mean Kd for [<sup>125</sup>I]-CGRP is 25.4 pM.
The IC<sub>50</sub> was defined as the concentration of a compound of invention required to displace 50% of radioligand binding. 
Non-specific binding was defined with 1 μΜ beta-CGRP (Bachem). 
Final assay concentration of [<sup>125</sup>I]-CGRP was 18 pM.
